            <description><![CDATA[【家长注意！7月深圳120接诊溺水14宗，一半是孩子<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】暑假期间孩子游泳、戏水等引发的溺水事故易发、高发！据深圳120调度数据显示，7月1日以来，深圳120共接溺水报警14人次，其中有7人为4～17岁的未成年人。阿卫提醒：家长们一定要增强安全意识和监护意识，加强对孩子的防溺水安全教育👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%237%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3120%E6%8E%A5%E6%BA%BA%E6%B0%B4%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A614%E5%AE%97%23&amp;extparam=%237%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3120%E6%8E%A5%E6%BA%BA%E6%B0%B4%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A614%E5%AE%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#7月以来深圳120接溺水报警14宗#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg4if3i42yj20u00wqjvx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg4if2z8ndj20nd0pqgul.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg4if4bdsdj20fn0kun8z.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg4itx3u2hj20u01m5dpg.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
